        <DisplayName>ScrollWithStationaryCursor</DisplayName>
        <Description xml:space="preserve">Adds commands that allow to scroll up or down in the text editor while having the (keyboard) cursor move along. For every line that you scroll up, the cursor will move one line up, and similarly when scrolling down. Because the cursor moves along as you scroll, it will remain the same distance from the top or bottom of the editor during the process.</Description>
    </Metadata>
